## General ID Format

**Pattern:** `[context]-[element]-[purpose/type]`

**Components:**
- **Context:** The resource or feature (`user`, `article`, `comment`, `nav`, `modal`)
- **Element:** The specific element (`login`, `title`, `body`, `toggle`, `menu`)
- **Purpose/Type:** The element type or function (`form`, `input`, `button`, `link`, `container`, `section`)

**Examples:**
- `user-login-form` = user context + login element + form type
- `article-title-input` = article context + title element + input type
- `nav-home-link` = nav context + home element + link type

